  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这套工业物联网赛车游戏系统画一张架构图。核心是用一个主控制器来驱动整个游戏循环，你觉得怎么开始比较好？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，您说的主控制器是IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController对吧？然后它直接驱动PLC逻辑层来管理游戏状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Main到Game是核心控制流。接下来Game需要把渲染指令发出去，这里有个TelemetryStream负责数据可视化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Game指向ThreeScene，标注上\"Renderiza\"。然后ThreeScene作为渲染层，需要关联具体的显示对象吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，ThreeScene要同时挂Car和Track，一个是车辆模型，一个是赛道环境。另外Game本身还需要导入这两个资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有点绕，ThreeScene关联Car和Track我理解，但Game也要分别指向它们？用\"Importa\"标注？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Game用\"Importa\"拉取Car和Track的资源定义，ThreeScene则是实际渲染实例。这是数据层和表现层的分离。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Car",
        "Track",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，已添加Game到Car和Track的导入关系。现在游戏还需要哪些子系统？物理引擎？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Physics用MQTT_Broker做消息中转，Game通过Hook机制订阅物理事件。同样Controls和Camera也要Hook进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Physics是MQTT_Broker，Controls是EdgeNode，Camera是PLC_Logic——这三个类型都不一样，但都用\"Hook\"连到Game？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera",
        "Game"
